title: Fa'ato'ialemanu
text:
Fa'ato'ialemanu is a village on the island of <a href="Upolu">Upolu</a> in <a href="Samoa">Samoa</a>. It is situated on the north central side of the island and is part of the greater <a href="Apia">Apia</a> area. The village has a population of 841.
The village is in the political district of <a href="Tuamasaga">Tuamasaga</a>.
